# Per-sample noise from visual eval pipelines (multiple layouts exist):
# - full eval: eval_*/policies/<policy>/episodes/<seq>/* and eval_*/cases/<seq>/*
# - selected-cases eval: eval_*/eval_*/episodes/<policy>__<seq>/* and eval_*/eval_*/cases/<seq>/*
# All contain thousands of small per-sample JSON/CSV files. Aggregated reports/
# + top-level summary.json/episodes.json/episodes.csv are sufficient.
ShapeNBV/eval_*/**/episodes/
ShapeNBV/eval_*/**/cases/
ShapeNBV/eval_*/**/comparisons/

